OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry and bright in the
OL,6,Fmorning with just the odd shower.
OL,7,FOutbreaks of rain will spread
OL,8,Fnortheast during late afternoon. Warm,
OL,9,Fespecially in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome showery and mainly light
OL,12,Frain will clear east through the
OL,13,Fevening. Then it will stay dry
OL,14,Fovernight but with low cloud pushing
OL,15,Finto the southwest.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FIt will be largely cloudy
OL,18,Fthrough the day with some showery
OL,19,Foutbreaks of rain which may turn heavy
OL,20,Fat times, but some brighter spells may
OL,21,Fdevelop in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
