OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Sunday with a chance of showers.
OL,7,FSunny spells and a few showers on
OL,8,FMonday and Tuesday. Remaining cooler
OL,9,Fthan recent days.
